					'Sorry piggies but that's a necessary sacrifice'
					'''
			}

			AbsoluteTVRemote: {
				DisplayName: Absolute TV Remote
				Tooltip:
					'''
					<left> to generate an aura around you that slows down projectiles in radius on a 2 minute cooldown
					<right> to generate an aura that instead speeds up projectiles in radius, also on a 2 minute cooldown
					Pressing {0} will fire a projectile that pauses enemies in their tracks, usable on a 5 minute cooldown
					'TV NEVER DIES!'
					'''
			}

			PlanetShaper: {
				DisplayName: Planet Shaper
				Tooltip:
					'''
					This scythe is swung directionally instead of spun
					Has a three-swing combo:
					    Every first swing, the scythe shoots one homing fireball and 2 cosmic beams
					    Every second swing, the scythe shoots one cosmic beam and two homing fireballs
					    Every third swing, the scythe is spun around
					    While spun, emits up to six homing fireballs and cosmic beams
					The scythe and fireballs ignore 125 points of defense and inflict [iabuff:CalamityMod/Dragonfire]
					The cosmic beams ignore 75 points of defense and inflict both [iabuff:CalamityMod/ElementalMix] and [iabuff:CatalystMod/AstralBlight]
					'LADIES AND GENTLEMAN... LET IT ROCK LET IT ROCK LET IT ROCK!!!'
					'''
			}

			GodsPitch: {
				DisplayName: God's Pitch
				Tooltip:
					'''
					Increases maximum inspiration by 5
					15% increased symphonic damage
					Increases the duration of your symphonic empowerments by 3 seconds
					Increases the level of empowerments you apply to yourself and others by 2
					Increases empowerment range
					Instrument attacks launch pipes upward that eventually fall down
					[c/FF232C:The pipes sound effects are loud and may be startling or otherwise bad for some]
					'Your ears are not worthy to hear this...'
					'''
			}

			GauntletofAnnihilationVoid: {
				DisplayName: Gauntlet of Annihilation
				Tooltip:
					'''
					<left> will unlease a flurry of 4 cosmic gauntlets that inflict [cbuff:CalamityMod/GodSlayerInferno]
					<right> will release rapid cosmic punches and lunge you in the direction of the mouse
					Lunging only consumes half the void cost and on collision during the lunge, you are knocked back
					Pressing <left> 3 frames after being knocked back will release a God Slaying Gauntlet
					The God Slaying Gauntlet always crits and also inflicts [cbuff:CalamityMod/WhisperingDeath]
					Provides a light source while favorited in the inventory
					'''
			}

			GauntletofAnnihilation: {
				DisplayName: Gauntlet of Annihilation
				Tooltip:
					'''
					<left> will unlease a flurry of 4 cosmic gauntlets that inflict [cbuff:CalamityMod/GodSlayerInferno]
					<right> will release rapid cosmic punches and lunge you in the direction of the mouse
					On collision during the lunge, you are knocked back
					Pressing <left> 3 frames after being knocked back will release a God Slaying Gauntlet
					The God Slaying Gauntlet always crits and also inflicts [cbuff:CalamityMod/WhisperingDeath]
					Provides a light source while favorited in the inventory
					'''
			}

			BlightedBadge: {
				DisplayName: Blighted Badge
				Tooltip:
					'''
					True melee strikes drops astral stars from the sky
					Attackers are shocked, dealing immense damage
					Taking damage will massively increase melee speed and critical strike chance briefly
					Also releases an explosion and temporarily increases true melee damage by 30% when damaged
					Boost duration scales with the amount of damage you took, up to 10 seconds
					Nullifies the Astral Infection debuff
					'''
			}

			ImagiknightHeraldry: {
				DisplayName: Imagiknight Heraldry
				Tooltip:
					'''
					Multiplies all damage based on how close you are to teammates, with a maximum damage boost of 20%
					Emit a blazing aura that also boosts the damage of teammates
					Teammates gain increasing multiplicative damage the closer they are to you
					These multipliers do not stack with the [i:CalamityMod/WarbanneroftheRighteous] Warbanner of the Righteous multiplier, and the higher bonus of the two will be used
					Effects are transparent and silent if visibility is disabled
					Gives all teammates +{0} HP/s life regen, +{1}% max life, {2}% damage reduction, {3} defense and {4}% increased damage
					'An idea is a mere particle, one that exponentially accelerates the more minds it travels through.
					When you put enough minds together, they can make said idea truly unstoppable.' -Imagiknight_Girus
					'''
			}

			VibrantShield: {
				DisplayName: Vibrant Shield
				Tooltip:
					'''
					Increases max void by 25
					You constantly generate a 15 life shield
					'''
			}

			DivineAxe: {
				DisplayName: Divine Axe
				Tooltip:
					'''
					Swings a slow and heavy axe that is infused with [cbuff:CalamityMod/HolyFlames]
					On a direct hit with the axe, it summons a star shaped explosion which inflicts [cbuff:Daybreak]
					<right>ing summons a sun above you and while holding <right> you will stab at it, causing it to release large explosions
					These explosions inflict [cbuff:Daybreak]
					'''
			}

			AncientSteelShield: {
				DisplayName: Ancient Steel Shield
				Tooltip:
					'''
					You constantly generate a 20 life shield
					Attackers have a chance to be afflicted with a stacking, permanent bleed for 5 damage per second
					This chance increases with your critical strike chance
					'''
			}

			DoubleFlail: {
				DisplayName: Double Flail-Core
				Tooltip:
					'''
					75% basic damage
					Flail weapons on first hit and for a chance every further hit create either a brimstone or blizzard spike ball
					The Brimstone spike ball applies [cbuff:CalamityMod/BrimstoneFlames] to enemies and rarely grants the [iabuff:InfernalEclipseWeaponsDLC/HotFlailDmg] buff
					The Blizzard spike ball applies [iabuff:Frostburn2] to enemies and rarely grants the [iabuff:InfernalEclipseWeaponsDLC/ColdFlailDefense] buff
					'''
			}

			PerfectPurple: {
				DisplayName: Cosmic Perfection Flail-Core
				Tooltip:
					'''
					100% basic damage
					Flail weapons on first hit create a perfect spike ball
					Further flail hits have a chance to create more perfect spike balls
					Perfect spike balls inflict [cbuff:CalamityMod/GodSlayerInferno] and rarely grant the [iabuff:InfernalEclipseWeaponsDLC/PerfectFlailBuff] buff
					'''
			}

			BlackHoleFlail: {
				DisplayName: Black Hole Flail-Core
				Tooltip:
					'''
					300% basic damage
					Flail weapon hits have a chance to create blackholes which home onto enemies, pulls enemies towards itself, and rarely inflicts [cbuff:CalamityMod/WitherDebuff]
					'This shouldn't work you know? A blackhole this size can absolutely destory the planet... I guess we shouldn't question it'
					'''
			}

			PerennialShield: {
				DisplayName: Perennial Shield
				Tooltip:
					'''
					You constantly generate a 50 life shield
					Gains extra effects depending on what Reaver Armor set bonus you have
					    [i:CalamityMod/ReaverHeadTank]: Increases max life by 15 and reduces damage taken by 10%
					    [i:CalamityMod/ReaverHeadMobility]: 10% increased movement speed and allows the ability to ram dash
					    [i:CalamityMod/ReaverHeadExplore]: 20% increased jump speed and grants fall damage immunity
					'''
			}

			HolyFlail: {
				DisplayName: Profaned Flail-Core
				Tooltip:
					'''
					100% basic damage
					Flail weapons on first hit create a profaned spike ball
					Further flail hits have a chance to create more profaned spike balls
					Profaned spike balls inflict [cbuff:CalamityMod/HolyFlames] and sometimes start holy fires on hit
					'''
			}

			TerraSheath: {
				DisplayName: Terra Sheath
				Tooltip:
					'''
					Sword strikes release {0} terra orbs that home into nearby enemies if held and not used for {1} {^1:second;seconds}
					These terra orbs recover 3% of you missing health upon hitting an enemy
					'''
			}

			BlazeScourgeBag: {
				DisplayName: Blaze Scourge Bag
				Tooltip:
					'''
					Gives the user master yoyo skills
					Secondary yoyos will do 50% less damage
					Your yoyo damage inflicts [cbuff:CalamityMod/HolyFlames] and has a chance to inflict [iabuff:InfernalEclipseWeaponsDLC/LimbBurn] on enemies
					Damaging an enemy with a yoyo will grant you 10% damage reduction until you take damage
					This effect must recharge for 15 seconds after protecting you
					'''
			}
		}

		ItemTooltip: {
			DuesFluteLore: They had found the source of the Astral Infection, and in a attempt to destroy it they used the Starcore on the infected altar.
			DuesFluteLore2: However, the altar had an unexpected reaction... two lights had started bouncing off each other heading the direction of the sky, opening a rift above it
			DuesFluteLore3: What came out of it was truly something out of this world, but they appreciation had to be cut short as the servant of the stars rushed towards them.
			UniversalLore1: Kos had made his final stand. Used all of his tricks up his sleeve. He had lost to them. However, it doesn't mean Eclipse had lost.
			UniversalLore2: Using every inch of power he had remaining in his soul, he summoned the true god slayer: The Devourer of Gods.
			ParallelLore1: To his expectation, they had slew the Storm Weaver. But Kos had another trick up his sleeve.
			ParallelLore2: Suddenly, with no warning, Kos had transported everyone to the mirror realm and called upon his second servant: Signus.
			TwoSideLore1: They overcame Ragnarok. They dismantled Eclipse. They survived the Slime Monsoon.
			TwoSideLore2: They stood at the brink of infinity, which only then Ren asked them "which path will you choose?"
			NeonRipperLore1: After the defeat of the Goliath, Erelian decided to repurpose some of the armor plating it wore.
			NeonRipperLore2: In doing so he created two weapons: the first of which being a scythe that could absorb aura, much like Kami's ability.
			PBGBardALore2: In doing so he created two weapons: the second of which being a guitar that shot colorful microwaves.
			DoubleFlailLore:
				'''
				Calamitas and Permafrost always had great teamwork as student and teacher when she was still a child
				These two Flails could be applying the same techniques to combine ice and fire in disasterous ways for your foes
				'''
			PerfectPurpleLore:
				'''
				Yet, it wasn't perfect.
				Teamwork can only take one so far. After all, you are your own best friend.
				Two of one, could do so much more because...
				You are perfect with yourself.
				'''
			SearingSpearTip: 150% basic damage
			ArcticSpearTip: 115% basic damage
			VerveineItem: "'An item from the orchid's blessing...'"
			EngineGatling:
				'''
				Gatling mode:
				Holding fire will gradually reduce weapon spread and increase fire rate to a cap
				Shots can pierce up to four times
				'''
			EngineGatlingMode: GATLING
			EngineLaser:
				'''
				Laser mode:
				Fires an infinitely piercing laser that leaves behind a trail of lingering damage
				The laser can bounce off tiles up to 3 times
				'''
			EngineLaserMode: LASER
			EngineTheBigOne:
				'''
				'The Big One' mode:
				Fires a massive orb of condensed energy that will detonate after some time
				The detonation will do more damage to foes closer to it's centre
				Only one 'Big One' can exist at a time
				'''
			EngineTheBigOneMode: THE BIG ONE
			Playtester: - Playtester Item -
			Contributor: - Contributor Item -
			Donor: - Donor Item -
			DedTo: - Dedicated to {0} -

			Dedicated: {
				Akira: Akira
				WH: WardrobeHummus
				Advantaje: Advantaje
